16:25.800 --> 16:29.667
Dialysis is basically where
a machine acts as your kidneys

16:29.667 --> 16:32.433
by taking blood out
of your body, cleaning it,

16:32.433 --> 16:33.934
and then returning it to you.

16:33.934 --> 16:36.600
Think of it as a Brita pitcher
