16:36.600 --> 16:40.300
which yes, is more disgusting
than I needed to make it sound.

16:40.300 --> 16:43.133
Dialysis can be a truly
exhausting process.

16:43.133 --> 16:44.900
Uh, you're typically
sitting in a chair,

16:44.900 --> 16:46.533
physically attached
to a machine

16:46.533 --> 16:48.700
for three four-hour sessions
a week.

16:48.700 --> 16:51.834
And Americans have been at
increasing risk of needing it,

16:51.834 --> 16:53.200
because chronic kidney disease

16:53.200 --> 16:55.166
is the ninth leading
cause of death

16:55.166 --> 16:56.934
in the United States.

16:56.934 --> 16:58.667
And while a lucky few
manage to get transplants,

16:58.667 --> 17:01.867
