on dialysis care,

17:07.934 --> 17:10.433
we have one of
the industrialized world's

17:10.433 --> 17:11.900
highest mortality rates.

17:11.900 --> 17:13.166
So we're spending the most

17:13.166 --> 17:15.300
to essentially get the least.

17:15.300 --> 17:17.867
We're basically paying for
a fully-loaded Lamborghini

17:17.867 --> 17:21.300
