28:25.867 --> 28:28.133
DaVita would pick out doctors

28:28.133 --> 28:29.567
and physicians' groups

28:29.567 --> 28:32.133
who cared for
a large number of patients

28:32.133 --> 28:34.100
who had renal disease,

28:34.100 --> 28:36.000
and then it would offer them
lucrative deals

28:36.000 --> 28:39.266
to refer patients to
their dialysis clinics.

