30:27.600 --> 30:28.767
an A-Rod.

30:28.767 --> 30:32.133
Uh, and a--and a separate case

30:32.133 --> 30:34.500
accused them not so much
of throwing extra drugs

30:34.500 --> 30:37.033
into the trash
