30:37.033 --> 30:39.367
And then involved something
called Epogen,

30:39.367 --> 30:41.367
a medication used
to raise a patient's

30:41.367 --> 30:43.066
red blood cell count.

30:43.066 --> 30:44.867
A whistleblower said
the DaVita personnel

30:44.867 --> 30:46.967
referred to it as "liquid gold."

30:46.967 --> 30:48.266
And with good reason.

30:48.266 --> 30:50.300
At one point,
it accounted for a quarter

30:50.300 --> 30:51.867
of the company's revenue

30:51.867 --> 30:54.567
and up to 40% of its earnings,

30:54.567 --> 30:56.200
although it was
later discovered

30:56.200 --> 30:58.000
that at the higher dosage levels

30:58.000 --> 30:59.166
that DaVita was using,

30:59.166 --> 31:01.100
there was no solid evidence

31:01.100 --> 31:03.200
that Epogen made people
feel better,

31:03.200 --> 31:07.133
improved survival, or had
any clinical benefit at all,

31:07.133 --> 31:09.734
which is incidentally
also the new tagline

31:09.734 --> 31:11.567
for this television show,

31:11.567 --> 31:12.800
and it seems fair.

31:12.800 --> 31:16.233
It seems harsh
but increasingly fair.

31:16.233 --> 31:19.266
And--and I--I think you know
what is coming now.

31:19.266 --> 31:21.333
DaVita denied any wrongdoing

31:21.333 --> 31:24.767
and settled that lawsuit
for $55 million.

31:24.767 --> 31:26.633
And DaVita will say that
they keep settling cases

31:26.633 --> 31:29.000
because they can't afford
to get shut out from Medicare,

31:29.000 --> 31:30.233
but the fact remains,

31:30.233 --> 31:32.333
just the three cases
I have mentioned

31:32.333 --> 31:35.266
in the last five years have
resulted in them paying out

31:35.266 --> 31:38.033
nearly a billion dollars
in settlements.

31:38.033 --> 31:39.834
And that doesn't exactly
give you confidence

31:39.834 --> 31:41.066
in their product.

31:41.066 --> 31:42.834
If the Fleshlight company

31:42.834 --> 31:45.200
