Suggesting that
the cozy atmosphere

35:03.367 --> 35:05.166
of a DaVita dialysis center

35:05.166 --> 35:08.033
is a valid reason to turn down
a kidney transplant

35:08.033 --> 35:10.066
is the moral equivalent
